User Table:
| id (PK) | username | password | other_fields |
Post Table:
| id (PK) | other_fields |
Comment Table:
| id (PK) | post_id (FK) | parent_comment_id (FK) | user_id (FK) | content | other_fields |
Like Table:
| id (PK) | comment_id (FK) | user_id (FK) | other_fields |
Dislike Table:
| id (PK) | comment_id (FK) | user_id (FK) | other_fields |
